-- This is auto-generated code
SELECT
    LocationID,
    COUNT(1) AS NUM_OF_RECORDS
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://marlabsdl.dfs.core.windows.net/nyc-taxi-data/raw/taxi_zone.csv',
        FORMAT = 'CSV',
        PARSER_VERSION = '1.0',
        FIRSTROW = 2
    ) 
     WITH (
        LocationID SMALLINT,
        Borough VARCHAR(15),
        Zone VARCHAR(50),
        service_zone VARCHAR(15)
    )AS [result]
GROUP BY LocationID
HAVING COUNT(1) > 1

-- -----------------------------------------------------------------

SELECT
    Borough,
    COUNT(1) AS NUM_OF_RECORDS
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://marlabsdl.dfs.core.windows.net/nyc-taxi-data/raw/taxi_zone.csv',
        FORMAT = 'CSV',
        PARSER_VERSION = '1.0',
        FIRSTROW = 2
    ) 
     WITH (
        LocationID SMALLINT,
        Borough VARCHAR(15),
        Zone VARCHAR(50),
        service_zone VARCHAR(15)
    )AS [result]
GROUP BY Borough
HAVING COUNT(1) > 1
